# Pulsegen Senior AI Engineer Assignment — Trend Analysis Agent

This repository implements the full assignment using an **Agentic AI pipeline** to extract, merge, clean, and trend Google Play Store reviews for Swiggy / Zomato from June 2024 → Today.

---

##  Key Features

 Daily batch ingestion  
 High-recall topic extraction agent (LLM)  
 Topic deduplication + merging agent  
 Topic taxonomy agent  
 Trend table generation (T-30 → T)  
 OpenAI API or Gemini API  
 Complete modular pipeline  

---

##  Architecture Overview

1. Ingestion Agent  
   Pulls reviews daily using `google_play_scraper`.

2. Extraction Agent  
   Uses LLM to extract short, high-recall issue topics from each review.

3. Merge Agent  
   Deduplicates similar topics using embeddings + clustering + LLM canonicalization.

4. Taxonomy Agent 
   Normalizes topics into consistent categories.

5. Trend Agent 
   Builds a T-30 to T trend table for all topics.

