##  How to Run

### 1. Install dependencies
```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 2. Set OpenAI Key
```
export OPENAI_API_KEY="your-key-here" or GEMINI_API_KEY="your-key-here"
```

### 3. Run pipeline
```
python main.py
```

Output will be saved in:

```
output/sample_report_T.csv
```

